-- Veer Energy Gains in Mumbai After Plan for Solar Panel Plant in Gujarat
-- B y   S u r e s h   S e s h a d r i
-- 2010-10-05T03:40:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/veer-energy-gains-in-mumbai-after-plan-for-solar-panel-plant-in-gujarat.html
Veer Energy & Infrastructure Ltd.
climbed in Mumbai trading after the Indian wind-power developer
said it plans to set up a plant for manufacturing
10 megawatts of solar panels a year in the western state of
Gujarat.  The shares rose 2.2 percent to 9.16 rupees as of 9:09 a.m.
local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
